<https://acme.example/knowledge/playbooks/data-freshness-incident> <http://schema.org/text> "# Trigger\n\nA freshness alert fires when [User Events](/tables/user-events.md) lags more than\n30 minutes behind its SLA.\n\n# Steps\n\n1. Check the ingestion job dashboard.\n2. Confirm whether [Weekly Active Users](/metrics/weekly-active-users.md) is affected.\n3. Escalate to the data platform on-call if lag exceeds 2 hours." .
<https://acme.example/knowledge/tables/user-events> <http://schema.org/text> "# Schema\n\n| Column        | Type      | Description                          |\n|---------------|-----------|--------------------------------------|\n| `event_id`    | STRING    | Globally unique event identifier.    |\n| `user_id`     | STRING    | The user who produced the event.     |\n| `event_name`  | STRING    | The type of event.                   |\n| `occurred_at` | TIMESTAMP | When the event occurred.             |\n\nPart of the [Events dataset](/datasets/events.md)." .
