<https://acme.example/knowledge/glossary/active-user> <http://schema.org/text> "# Definition\n\nAn **active user** is any `user_id` that produced at least one *qualifying event*\nduring the period under consideration. Used by the\n[Weekly Active Users](/metrics/weekly-active-users.md) metric." .
